{
  "stem": "18626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 302.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody of the Jews have any anger against the Jewish Committee, especially in Lithuania, because they couldn't help themselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was almost like a lotto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took these, these, and then-- and I'm sure they wiped their tears from their-- from their faces.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because they had to make a list to give out 800 people, or 2,000 people, or 500 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it was not plain people who did this type of work-- this type committee work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was all distinguished, educated, good-hearted people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm not talking about the Jewish police in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were already a different type of people, you know, some of them were real-- I mean poor elements.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, after the ghetto was established, they needed to know somebody Jewish people, you know, to keep control.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One Jew shouldn't rob from the other Jew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and the Jewish police had to do work for the committee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If the Germans wanted that and that street Jews to come to that place, to go to work to the airfield, the Jewish police used to knock in the doors.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rabinowitz, get up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's 6:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Your family is today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Your time to go to the airfield to work, to the airport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Germans were building an airport, and thousands of people had to work, taken to that slave labor work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the committee.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- The Jewish Committee gave out orders with little, you know, plaques, you know again on houses, who wants to be a Jewish policeman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there were a lot, you know, young, strong people, you know, with cool-- good maybe nerves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were not my age.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all older, you know, like-- but I don't think if I would be their age, maybe I would have nerve to be a policeman.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
